///////python project create by Django Framework////////////////////////////
1. create a new project folder
2. login project folder and create  main project
3. run project
4. create project application (login, registration, .....) in project folder
    but outside main project
5. connect application with main project

1. step: create project folder
-------------------------------------------
create project folder name "My_First_Project"

cd My_First_Project   //enter

2. step: create main project
-------------------------------------------
django-admin  startproject  My_First_Project

dir    //to see all info

3. step: run project
--------------------------------------------
python  manage.py  runserver

4. step: create project application(login, registration, ....) inside project folder
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
python  manage.py  startapp  registration

5. step: connect "registration" application with main project
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
a. go to main project --> settings.py

	INSTALLED_APPS = [
		.
		.
	   'registration',
	]
